{"tid":2234370,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"四大天王各捐款100萬 為電影基層人員紓困","createTime":"2020-10-08T00:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T00:55:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28e36e0dd3d244b9d6bbbbc67e3dad23f09efbc1","tid":2234370,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:20:04.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐下，今年香港約有近9成的影視製作人員冇工開，經濟陷入困境，古天樂、曾志偉與成龍等扯頭纜向10間電影公司籌旗拍抗疫片，另外，又得到劉鑾雄慈善基金也捐了1,000萬為電影基層人員紓困。據《蘋果》收到消息，其實還有幾十位演員有捐錢，如沒演出抗疫片的四大天王劉德華、張學友、郭富城和黎明，據知他們各自捐出100萬，算是出一分力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201008/VHHTKE4QXJG4FJGWNBLWSY6DXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201008%2FVHHTKE4QXJG4FJGWNBLWSY6DXU%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5IPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=101425cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201008%2FVHHTKE4QXJG4FJGWNBLWSY6DXU%2F&h=45aff98f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201008/VHHTKE4QXJG4FJGWNBLWSY6DXU/</a>"},{"pid":"e287c9470cbae3419654890d2eaebaff36ebdba7","tid":2234370,"uid":181819,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:30:57.000Z","msg":"學友雷曼事件輸咁多都仲要佢捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c625a18a25d7bfa588e9d09dd533cb555d8710ba","tid":2234370,"uid":268754,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e287c9470cbae3419654890d2eaebaff36ebdba7","tid":2234370,"uid":181819,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:30:57.000Z","msg":"學友雷曼事件輸咁多都仲要佢捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-